    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels at MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 1 for Class II device at MRL 2 with medium model influence. RH < 1.0 satisfied at all 5 operating conditions. Mesh independence confirmed with GCI 1.7%. Code verification demonstrates second-order accuracy. Validation evidence directly relevant to COU. Overall credibility assessment supports acceptance of CFD model for CPB hemolysis worst-case identification.",
